<template><Head title="Sign in"/><div class="design-auth"><aside class="design-auth-hero"><BrandLogo/><div><h1>Where talent meets opportunity.</h1><p>Show your game, connect with scouts and discover your next sporting opportunity.</p><div class="design-phone-card"><div class="design-phone-top"><span>RISING TALENT</span><i/></div><div class="design-phone-visual"><span class="design-phone-play"><Play fill="white"/></span><div class="design-live-stats"><div><strong>{{compact(views)}}</strong><small>Views</small></div><div><strong>{{compact(likes)}}</strong><small>Likes</small></div><div><strong>{{compact(followers)}}</strong><small>Followers</small></div></div></div><div class="design-phone-info"><strong>Lerato Ndlovu <b>✓</b></strong><span>Football · Midfielder · Soweto</span><p>Creative midfielder with vision, pace and high-intensity play.</p><div class="design-phone-progress"><i/></div></div></div></div><small>Talent. Opportunity. Community.</small></aside><section class="design-auth-form"><div class="design-auth-top"><span/><p>New here? <Link href="/register">Create account</Link></p></div><div class="design-form-inner"><h2>Welcome back</h2><p>Sign in to continue to your SportUniverse account.</p><form class="form-stack" @submit.prevent="submit"><label><span class="su-label">Email or phone number</span><span class="auth-input-icon"><Mail/><input v-model="form.login" class="su-input" autocomplete="username" placeholder="name@example.com"/></span><small v-if="form.errors.login" class="error">{{form.errors.login}}</small></label><label><span class="su-label">Password</span><span class="auth-input-icon"><LockKeyhole/><input v-model="form.password" class="su-input" type="password" autocomplete="current-password" placeholder="Enter your password"/><Eye class="input-end"/></span><small v-if="form.errors.password" class="error">{{form.errors.password}}</small></label><div class="login-options"><label><input v-model="form.remember" type="checkbox"/> Remember me</label><Link